TY  - JOUR
TI  - Tests of Equality Between Sets of Coefficients in Two Linear Regressions
AU  - Chow, Gregory C.
AB  - [Having estimated a linear regression with p coefficients, one may wish to test whether m additional observations belong to the same regression. This paper presents systematically the tests involved, relates the prediction interval (for m = 1) and the analysis of covariance (for m > p) within the framework of general linear hypothesis (for any m), and extends the results to testing the equality between subsets of coefficients.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jul., 1960
