TY  - JOUR
TI  - Stability of Equilibrium and the Value of Positive Excess Demand
AU  - McKenzie, Lionel W.
AB  - [Global stability is proved for a dynamic competitive model with the assumption that goods are weak gross substitutes. Then local stability is proved when this assumption is weakened. A new Liapounov function is introduced.]
